    10→ *  1. Load configuration and input email data with disambiguated candidate scores
    11→ *  2. Rank all categories by final score (highest to lowest)
    12→ *  3. Select primary label (highest scoring category above confidence threshold)
    13→ *  4. Select secondary labels based on gap rules and allowed combinations
