    15→ *  6. Create final label selection with confidence and subtype assignments
    16→ *  7. Pass selected labels to AI routing stage
    17→ *
    18→ * DATABASE OPERATIONS
    19→ *  - None (pure business logic node)
    20→ *  - Database persistence handled by separate prepare_multi_label_persistence node
    21→ *
    22→ * EXPECTED INPUT (from DisambiguationNode)
