    25→ *  - detected_attributes: [{attribute_name, attribute_value, influence_role, ...}]
    26→ *  - stage_id from disambiguation stage
    27→ *
    28→ * OUTPUT FORMAT
    29→ *  Email objects with selected labels for AI routing:
    30→ *  [{
