    59→ *  - Primary Label: Highest scoring category above minimum threshold (default: 3)
    60→ *  - Secondary Labels: Within configured gap of primary (default: 2 points) and above minimum confidence
    61→ *  - Allowed Combinations: Explicit whitelist (e.g., financial+actionable)
